cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about improving the efficiency and accuracy of semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a knowledge distillation method, which is a common technique in machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper utilizes a pre-trained autoencoder and non-local interactions, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on popular benchmarks, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
